CATEGORY=Special Ability|Background ~ Cultist.MOD	DESC:You were once a part of a cult to a dark deity or other rivalling power such as an Archdevil, Archfey, Demon Lord, Elder Evil, Old One, or Primordial. The dark practices you took part in has provided you with insight into obscure knowledge of deities, rivalling powers and the ability to keep secrets. Whatever the nature of the cult you were a part of, you may have been groomed for an important purpose or been a reluctant participant. You could have left amicably, fled after coming to your senses, or been forced out after a conflict with other members of the cult.
CATEGORY=Special Ability|Background ~ Survivor.MOD	DESC:You are a survivor, you have endured in circumstances where others have perished. The experience you survived may have been a natural, supernatural, or magical disaster, the rampage of some kind of monster, or violence prejudice. You may be haunted by your experiences or rouse into action by them, either way your past trauma is part of you and has driven you to adventure.
